{
   "info" : "<table width=\"100%\" summary=\"page for nottem\"><tr><td>nottem</td><td style=\"text-align: right;\">R Documentation</td></tr></table>\\n<h2>\\nAverage Monthly Temperatures at Nottingham, 1920&ndash;1939\\n</h2>\\n<h3>Description</h3>\\n<p>A time series object containing average air temperatures at\\nNottingham Castle in degrees Fahrenheit for 20 years.\\n</p>\\n<h3>Usage</h3>\\n<pre>nottem</pre>\\n<h3>Source</h3>\\n<p>Anderson, O. D. (1976)\\n<em>Time Series Analysis and Forecasting: The Box-Jenkins approach.</em>\\nButterworths. Series R.\\n</p>\\n<h3>Examples</h3>\\n<pre>\\nrequire(stats); require(graphics)\\nnott &lt;- window(nottem, end = c(1936,12))\\nfit &lt;- arima(nott, order = c(1,0,0), list(order = c(2,1,0), period = 12))\\nnott.fore &lt;- predict(fit, n.ahead = 36)\\nts.plot(nott, nott.fore$pred, nott.fore$pred+2*nott.fore$se,\\n        nott.fore$pred-2*nott.fore$se, gpars = list(col = c(1,1,4,4)))\\n</pre>\\n",
